info.symbol_desc_content: GMCI 30 represents a selection of the top 30 cryptocurrencies, excluding stablecoins and gas tokens. With majors like BTC, ETH, and SOL, the index provides a solid foundation for gaining exposure to the mainstream crypto landscape.

GMCI L2 tracks leading Layer 2 blockchain networks. Layer 2 assets focus on scalability and innovation, and have become increasingly popular with many decentralized apps now seeking cheaper and faster alternatives to Ethereum.

GMCI MEME contains the leading meme coins by market capitalization. With many memecoins lacking clear fundamentals, GMCI MEME provides traders with a simple solution to gaining exposure to the popular vertical
